<body>
	<div>
		<milestone n="titre-prologue" />
		<pb n="33v" /><cb n="2" />
				<head type="initial">In sancti Barnabe apostoli.</head>
		<milestone n="prologue" />
		<p>
			<seg place="inline" hand="manus1" type="lectio"><lb n="15" break="no"/>Lectio ia</seg>
			Barnabas hebrayce,<lb n="16" />
			latine interpretatur filius<lb n="17" />
			prophetȩ uel filius consolati<lb n="18" break="no"/>onis.
			Barnabas qui et Ioseph na<lb n="19" break="no"/>tione
			Cyprie ciuitatis ex Cyro re<lb n="20" break="no"/>ge
			Persarum fundata extitit,  cum<lb n="21" />
			Paulo ingentibus apostolatum a<lb n="22" break="no"/>deptus
			est. Deinde propter Iohannem<lb n="23" />
			discipulum qui etiam cognomen<lb n="24" break="no"/>to
			Marcus appellatur  seiunctus<lb n="25" />
			a Paulo,  nichilominus euange<lb n="26" break="no"/>lice
			predicationis sibi opus in<lb n="27" break="no"/>iunctum
			exercuit,  martirio co<lb n="28" break="no"/>ronatus.
			Cuius festiuitas cele<lb n="29" break="no"/>bratur
			tercio ydus iunii.
		</p>
</div>
